  "description": "<h1>Active: Soul Release</h1> Provides %soul_heal_amount% health regeneration when cast on allies.<br><br>Can be ground targeted to lie dormant for up to %ground_duration%s and attach to the first enemy that comes within %latch_range% radius. When on enemies, deals %soul_damage_amount% damage per second and provides True Sight over them and shares their vision with the wearer's team.<br><br>Lasts %duration% seconds.<br><br>Gains charges every time an enemy hero dies within %soul_radius% units.",
  "notes": [
    "Empty distillers gain 2 charges.",
    "Only the closest Essence Distiller to the dying hero will gain a charge.",
    "If the allied unit is attacked by an enemy hero or Roshan, the effect is lost.",
    "Does not trigger spell block or spell reflect.",
    "While dormant, provides vision in %latch_vision% radius. Vision lingers for %linger_after_latch_duration%s after latching."
  ],
